Analysis proposals, research reports and regulations from other governments, non-government organizations and the private sector to understand trends;
Use of Microsoft Word, Excel, Access, Visual Basic and/or SQL for analysing data and developing reports;
Support team members and participate in team activities to analyse environmental and economic impacts from transportation; et
